name: CypherWorX
overview:
CypherWorX®, Inc. is a New York-based e-Learning solutions company that partners with small businesses and nonprofit corporations worldwide.

CypherWorX®, Inc. partners with business-to-business, association and CRM clients by providing holistic e-Learning solutions. These range from course development to Learning Management System (LMS) integration under the brand names NP Training Works™ and CollaborNation®. The company provides the standard branded NP Training Works™ LMS or the CollaborNation® Collaborative Learning Environment® which combines social learning and social media.

The LMS content ranges from industry- and government-required training to general business and professional development learning opportunities. This content is delivered through different outlets including self-directed and instructor-led e-Learning Courses, Webinars, and learner-generated resources and groups. These products are distinguished by their active learning environments that address a variety of learning styles.
